 \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"Notre-Dame Cathedral\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Seine's historical significance includes the 841 Viking plundering of Neustria, the burning of Rouen, and the siege of France.\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2187, \"end\": 2192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.50204504700196e-29, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2257, \"end\": 2265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neustria\", \"score\": 0.999999970636964, \"rank\": 2.9363036079754043e-08, \"text\": \"Neustria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neustria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neustria\"}, {\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.651279601713642e-18, \"text\": \"Rouen\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouen\"}, {\"begin\": 2306, \"end\": 2312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996102568115715, \"rank\": 0.0003898673783341592, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 841 Viking plundering\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"the burning\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"the siege\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The river has influenced the numbering of Parisian streets, with perpendicular or oblique streets starting their numbers from the side closest to the Seine and parallel streets numbering in the direction of the current.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2465, \"end