\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.50204504700196e-29, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"highpollutionlevels\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, ParisOlympics2024 preparations included a clean-up operation to make it usable for the Games and further showcase the city.\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2830}, {\"ngram\": \"a clean-up operation\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the tests were carried out on July 26, results showed the water quality in the Seine was slightly below the standards needed to authorise swimming.\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3010, \"end\": 3015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.50204504700196e-29, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2965}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"the water quality\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"the standards\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daily water quality tests measure levels of fecal bacteria known as E. coli.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daily water quality tests measure levels\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"fecal bacteria\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Monitoring group Eau de Paris carried out the tests.\", \"from\": 315